# Creating wider age ranges to simplify 
# Proposed groups: 0 - 17, 18 - 29, 30 - 59, 60+
# Rationale: Under people more associated with crime; areas with children may be more likely to report crimes, seniors may
# be 'protectors of the community' by reporting any seen crime as they hangout in parks
# Male 2019
pop_2019_df['Male_0to17_2019'] = pop_2019_df['Male_Under_5'] + pop_2019_df['Male_5to9'] + pop_2019_df['Male_10to14'] + pop_2019_df['Male_15to17']
pop_2019_df['Male_18to29_2019'] = pop_2019_df['Male_18to19'] + pop_2019_df['Male_20'] + pop_2019_df['Male_21'] + pop_2019_df['Male_22to24'] + pop_2019_df['Male_25to29']
pop_2019_df['Male_30to59_2019'] = pop_2019_df['Male_30to34'] + pop_2019_df['Male_35to39'] + pop_2019_df['Male_40to44'] + pop_2019_df['Male_45to49'] + pop_2019_df['Male_50to54'] + pop_2019_df['Male_55to59']
pop_2019_df['Male_Over60_2019'] = pop_2019_df['Male_60to61'] + pop_2019_df['Male_62to64'] + pop_2019_df['Male_65to66'] + pop_2019_df['Male_67to69'] + pop_2019_df['Male_70to74'] + pop_2019_df['Male_75to79'] + pop_2019_df['Male_80to84'] + pop_2019_df['Male_85_Over']
# Female 2019
pop_2019_df['Female_0to17_2019'] = pop_2019_df['Female_Under_5'] + pop_2019_df['Female_5 to 9 years'] + pop_2019_df['Female_10to14'] + pop_2019_df['Female_15to17']
pop_2019_df['Female_18to29_2019'] = pop_2019_df['Female_18to19'] + pop_2019_df['Female_20'] + pop_2019_df['Female_21'] + pop_2019_df['Female_22to24'] + pop_2019_df['Female_25to29']
pop_2019_df['Female_30to59_2019'] = pop_2019_df['Female_30to34'] + pop_2019_df['Female_35to39'] + pop_2019_df['Female_40to44'] + pop_2019_df['Female_45to49'] + pop_2019_df['Female_50to54'] + pop_2019_df['Female_55to59']
pop_2019_df['Female_Over60_2019'] = pop_2019_df['Female_60to61'] + pop_2019_df['Female_62to64'] + pop_2019_df['Female_65to66'] + pop_2019_df['Female_67to69'] + pop_2019_df['Female_70to74'] + pop_2019_df['Female_75to79'] + pop_2019_df['Female_80to84'] + pop_2019_df['Female_85_Over']

# Calculating CVs
# Male
pop_2019_df['Male_0to17_2019_CV'] = pop_2019_df['Male_0to17_2019_SE'] / pop_2019_df['Male_0to17_2019'] * 100
pop_2019_df['Male_18to29_2019_CV'] = pop_2019_df['Male_18to29_2019_SE'] / pop_2019_df['Male_18to29_2019'] * 100
pop_2019_df['Male_30to59_2019_CV'] = pop_2019_df['Male_30to59_2019_SE'] / pop_2019_df['Male_30to59_2019'] * 100
pop_2019_df['Male_Over60_2019_CV'] = pop_2019_df['Male_Over60_2019_SE'] / pop_2019_df['Male_Over60_2019'] * 100
# Female
pop_2019_df['Female_0to17_2019_CV'] = pop_2019_df['Female_0to17_2019_SE'] / pop_2019_df['Female_0to17_2019'] * 100
pop_2019_df['Female_18to29_2019_CV'] = pop_2019_df['Female_18to29_2019_SE'] / pop_2019_df['Female_18to29_2019'] * 100
pop_2019_df['Female_30to59_2019_CV'] = pop_2019_df['Female_30to59_2019_SE'] / pop_2019_df['Female_30to59_2019'] * 100
pop_2019_df['Female_Over60_2019_CV'] = pop_2019_df['Female_Over60_2019_SE'] / pop_2019_df['Female_Over60_2019'] * 100

pop_2019_df = pop_2019_df.drop(['Male_0to17_2019_SE', 'Male_18to29_2019_SE', 'Male_30to59_2019_SE', 'Male_Over60_2019_SE',
                               'Female_0to17_2019_SE', 'Female_18to29_2019_SE', 'Female_30to59_2019_SE', 'Female_Over60_2019_SE'],axis=1)
